        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>E-SIGN Modernization Act of 2022 </b></p> <p>This bill repeals certain requirements regarding the use of electronic records in commerce. Specifically, the bill repeals the requirement that consumers must demonstrate their ability to access information electronically in order to consent to the use of electronic records. </p>]]>
        </text>
